text: Hi,   I keep getting  ERROR:  syntax error at or near "INSERT" LINE 5:   INSERT INTO staff.VALUES (1,"test");            ^ ********** Error **********  ERROR: syntax error at or near "INSERT" SQL state: 42601 Character: 69  Why is this ? Please help ?

author: @LoKKcHA
text: You should probably let people know that PostgrSQL looks at double quotes differently than single quotes.  I was scratching my head at that error for a while.  Here's a stackoverflow answer that helped me: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12428496/cannot-get-simple-postgresql-insert-to-work
